Tidy Models keeps you safe. The process of machine learning has many pitfalls or potholes

00:10:27.460 --> 00:10:32.580
in the road on the way, if you will, and what Tidy Models is designed to help you

00:10:32.580 --> 00:10:40.580
avoid those pitfalls, those potholes. So Max, let's start with talking about being

00:10:40.580 --> 00:10:46.900
more ergonomic. How do you think about being ergonomic when it comes to modeling?

00:10:46.900 --> 00:10:51.039
So a lot of times I think about physical ergonomics. When I work in diagnostics, we have people

00:10:51.039 --> 00:10:55.299
come in with clinicians, and they would interact with the diagnostic machines we had, and we'd

00:10:55.299 --> 00:10:59.859
watch them and see, just as they did their work, what were things they did over and over

00:10:59.859 --> 00:11:04.099
again or they might get frustrated with. And there's a lot of that in the syntax, the

00:11:04.099 --> 00:11:08.260
way we design syntax for our functions. But in particular in machine learning, there's

00:11:08.260 --> 00:11:12.260
an extra layer of things that we have to think about, because there's a high amount of cognitive

00:11:12.260 --> 00:11:15.419
load for machine learning. So when you go to do a model for the first

